snippet.title: Forza Customs - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Forza Customs is a mobile car-themed puzzle game developed by Hutch Games Ltd. Players will solve puzzles to help design, customize, and tune a car specifically to the players liking. Restore iconic cars from paint to body parts to create the ultimate car. Forza Customs is available now for iOS and Android.

#Gaming #Forza #IGN
